{"word":"στοιχάς","slug":"στοιχάς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n96924\" key=\"stoixa/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">στοιχάς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">άδος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">στοῖχος</etym>) <sense id=\"n96924.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in a row one behind another</tr_>, esp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἱ Στοιχάδες</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νῆσοι</foreign>), name of the islands which lie <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in a row</tr_> east of Toulon, now <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">les Îles d' Hyères</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:554\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.554</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:1:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.1.10</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n96924.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐλᾶαι ς</foreign>. olive-trees (prob. because planted <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in rows</tr_>) which were not sacred, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">like</abbr> the <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μορίαι</foreign>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sol.\">Sol.</a></author> </bibl> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:5:36\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.36</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0583.tlg001:62\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philoch.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">62</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n96924.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στοιχάς, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen></foreign>, an aromatic plant, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cassidony, Lavandula Stoechas</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0579.tlg002:918\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Orph.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">918</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dsc.\">Dsc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.26</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}